msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/name"
msgid "Arnhem Hell"
msgstr "El infierno de Arnhem"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/name_big"
msgid "Arnhem Hell"
msgstr "El infierno de Arnhem"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"You can be proud of yourself; you did everything you possibly could, despite "
"the odds and poor planning on the part of supreme command. The Germans are "
"duly impressed with your courage and tenacity. If only this operation would "
"have been properly planned..."
msgstr ""
"Puedes estar orgulloso de ti mismo; hiciste todo lo que pudiste, a pesar de "
"las adversidades y la mala planificación por parte del alto mando. Los "
"alemanes están muy impresionados con tu valentía y tenacidad. Si tan solo "
"esta operación se hubiera planificado adecuadamente..."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"In the end, there was no way in which you could have held the position at "
"the bridge. Lacking firepower and proper means of communication, plus very "
"poor planning, this outcome was predictable; but your courage will be "
"remembered."
msgstr ""
"Al final, no había forma de que pudieras mantener la posición en el puente. "
"Sin potencia de fuego ni medios de comunicación adecuados, además de una "
"planificación muy deficiente, este resultado era previsible; pero tu "
"valentía será recordada."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/date"
msgid "September 17th, 1944 · Arnhem, Netherlands"
msgstr "17 de septiembre de 1944 · Arnhem, Países Bajos"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/place"
msgid "1st Airborne Division"
msgstr "1.ª División Aerotransportada"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/story"
msgid ""
"Operation Market Garden has begun!\n"
"\n"
"XXX Corps also started moving into the Netherlands from Belgium. They need "
"to cover the distance to Arnhem in a matter of days if they are to relieve "
"your unit at the Arnhem bridge.\n"
"\n"
"In the Nijmegen area, the US paratroopers will also attempt to capture the "
"bridges.\n"
"\n"
"You have marched from your dropzone to Arnhem proper in the meantime. The "
"Drop Zone, however, was miles away from the bridge you have to take; you "
"have been marching east along the river for a while now, wondering why there "
"isn't a single German to be seen.\n"
"\n"
"Your orders are to take the bridge and to hold it until XXX Corps arrives "
"from the south. It’s a relatively simple objective, but it will be hard to "
"achieve."
msgstr ""
"¡La operación Market Garden ha comenzado! El XXX Cuerpo también ha empezado "
"a avanzar hacia los Países Bajos desde Bélgica. Tienen que recorrer la "
"distancia que les separa de Arnhem en cuestión de días si quieren relevar a "
"tu unidad en el puente de Arnhem. En la zona de Nimega, los paracaidistas "
"estadounidenses también intentarán capturar los puentes.\n"
"\n"
"Mientras tanto, tú has marchado desde tu zona de salto hasta Arnhem. Sin "
"embargo, la zona de salto estaba a kilómetros de distancia del puente que "
"tienes que tomar; llevas un rato marchando hacia el este a lo largo del río, "
"preguntándote por qué no se ve ni un solo alemán. Tus órdenes son tomar el "
"puente y mantenerlo hasta que llegue el XXX Cuerpo desde el sur. Es un "
"objetivo relativamente sencillo, pero será difícil de lograr."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/attack_b_east"
msgid "Jerry is attacking our positions at the Eastern side of the bridge!"
msgstr "¡Jerry está atacando nuestras posiciones en el lado este del puente!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/attack_b_west"
msgid "Germans are pushing our positions at the Western side of the bridge!"
msgstr ""
"¡Los alemanes están presionando nuestras posiciones en el lado occidental "
"del puente!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/attack_district"
msgid "They are attacking the residential area!"
msgstr "¡Están atacando la zona residencial!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/attack_factory"
msgid "The enemy is attacking the factory facilities!"
msgstr "¡El enemigo está atacando las instalaciones de la fábrica!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/attack_hq"
msgid "Germans are attacking HQ! We cannot lose it!"
msgstr "¡Los alemanes están atacando el cuartel general! ¡No podemos perderlo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/attack_jeeppark"
msgid "Positions at the jeep park are under attack!"
msgstr "¡Las posiciones en el parque de jeeps están siendo atacadas!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/attack_post"
msgid "Our outpost is under attack!"
msgstr "¡Tu puesto avanzado está siendo atacado!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/attack_prison"
msgid "Another attack, it’s on the prison building!"
msgstr "¡Otro ataque, es contra el edificio de la prisión!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/attack_workshop"
msgid "The enemy is attacking our positions at the workshop facilities!"
msgstr ""
"¡El enemigo está atacando nuestras posiciones en las instalaciones del "
"taller!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/captured_b_east"
msgid "We’ve lost our positions at the Eastern side of the bridge!"
msgstr "¡Habéis perdido vuestras posiciones en el lado este del puente!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/captured_b_west"
msgid "The enemy has captured our positions at the Western side of the bridge!"
msgstr ""
"¡El enemigo ha capturado nuestras posiciones en el lado occidental del "
"puente!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/captured_district"
msgid "We’ve lost control over the residential area!"
msgstr "¡Habéis perdido el control sobre la zona residencial!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/captured_factory"
msgid ""
"Germans have captured our positions at the factory facilities! Fall back to "
"the Eastern side of the bridge!"
msgstr ""
"¡Los alemanes han tomado nuestras posiciones en las instalaciones de la "
"fábrica! ¡Retirada hacia el lado este del puente!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/captured_hq"
msgid "We’ve lost the HQ!"
msgstr "¡Hemos perdido el cuartel general!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/captured_jeeppark"
msgid "Germans have taken control over the jeep park!"
msgstr "¡Los alemanes han tomado el control del parque de jeeps!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/captured_post"
msgid "They have captured our outpost!"
msgstr "¡Han capturado vuestro puesto avanzado!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/captured_prison"
msgid "The prison building has been lost! Now they can strike right to our HQ!"
msgstr ""
"¡El edificio de la prisión se ha perdido! ¡Ahora pueden atacar directamente "
"vuestra sede central!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/captured_workshop"
msgid "Workshop facilities have been lost! Fall back to the prison building!"
msgstr ""
"¡Se han perdido las instalaciones del taller! ¡Retírate al edificio de la "
"prisión!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/6pd_lost_01"
msgid "We just lost one of our 6-pounders!"
msgstr "¡Acabamos de perder uno de nuestros cañones de 6 libras!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/6pd_lost_02"
msgid "The enemy has destroyed another 6-pounder! We have only one left!"
msgstr "¡El enemigo ha destruido otro cañón de 6 libras! ¡Solo nos queda uno!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/6pd_lost_03"
msgid "We’ve lost all our 6-pounders! Now we can count only on our PIATs!"
msgstr ""
"¡Hemos perdido todos nuestros cañones de 6 libras! ¡Ahora solo podemos "
"contar con nuestros PIAT!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/cutscene/intro_01"
msgid ""
"We’ve made it. Come on men, the bridge is not that far by now. Let’s keep "
"moving."
msgstr ""
"Lo hemos conseguido. Vamos, chicos, el puente ya no está muy lejos. Sigamos "
"adelante."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/cutscene/intro_02"
msgid ""
"Digby should have been here by now but I don’t think we can wait for him any "
"longer. I’m afraid we will have to handle this ourselves."
msgstr ""
"Digby ya debería estar aquí, pero no creo que podamos esperarlo más. Me temo "
"que tendremos que encargarnos de esto nosotros mismos."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/cutscene/intro_03"
msgid ""
"Hopefully, they will reach us by morning. Till then, we must control this "
"bridge. Lucky for us, looks like most of the Germans have gone, so we "
"shouldn’t meet tough resistance."
msgstr ""
"Con suerte, llegarán por la mañana. Hasta entonces, debemos controlar este "
"puente. Por suerte para nosotros, parece que la mayoría de los alemanes se "
"han ido, así que no deberíamos encontrar mucha resistencia."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/cutscene/intro_04"
msgid ""
"The bridge is ours now. Dig in, keep watch and get some rest. Digby had "
"better show up by morning…"
msgstr ""
"El puente ya es nuestro. Atacad, mantened la vigilancia y descansad un poco. "
"Más vale que Digby aparezca por la mañana..."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/secret01_hint"
msgid ""
"This appears to be one of the tanks which attacked us during the day, let's "
"see if it's still repairable."
msgstr ""
"Este parece ser uno de los tanques que nos atacaron durante el día, veamos "
"si aún se puede reparar."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/enemy_see_pl_tank"
msgid "Looks like we scared them to death with the tank."
msgstr "Parece que los asustamos muchísimo con el tanque."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/cutscene/morning_01"
msgid ""
"Beautiful morning, Colonel Frost. I hope your kits are not completely "
"soaked. The weather here is indeed not much different from our homelands."
msgstr ""
"Bonita mañana, coronel Frost. Espero que tus equipos no estén completamente "
"empapados. El tiempo aquí no difiere mucho del de nuestros países de origen."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/cutscene/morning_02"
msgid ""
"Good to see you, Major. The kits are fine which I cannot say about our "
"situation."
msgstr ""
"Me alegro de verte, comandante. Los equipos están bien, lo que no puedo "
"decir de nuestra situación."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/cutscene/morning_03"
msgid ""
"Thirty Corps is moving much slower than we’ve expected even in the worst "
"case scenario. It seems like we have to be ready for all possible German "
"counterattacks."
msgstr ""
"El 30.º Cuerpo avanza mucho más lentamente de lo que esperábamos, incluso en "
"el peor de los casos. Parece que tenemos que estar preparados para todos los "
"posibles contraataques alemanes."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/cutscene/morning_04"
msgid ""
"I believe we have everything we need, Colonel. The 6-pounders are rolling "
"out, AT specialists looking for ambush positions."
msgstr ""
"Creo que tenemos todo lo que necesitamos, coronel. Los cañones de 6 libras "
"están saliendo, los especialistas en armas antitanque buscan posiciones para "
"emboscadas."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/cutscene/morning_05"
msgid ""
"This might not be enough, I am afraid. The enemy cannot afford to lose this "
"bridge, otherwise their entire frontline will fall. They will throw "
"everything they have."
msgstr ""
"Me temo que eso podría no ser suficiente. El enemigo no puede permitirse "
"perder este puente, de lo contrario toda su línea del frente caerá. Lo darán "
"todo."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/cutscene/morning_06"
msgid ""
"This is going to be not easy for us but I am sure we will do it. The Corps "
"has some delay but they are not that far from us. I suggest discussing the "
"details in the HQ if you have any by far."
msgstr ""
"No va a ser fácil para nosotros, pero estoy seguro de que lo conseguiremos. "
"El Cuerpo tiene algo de retraso, pero no están muy lejos de nosotros. "
"Sugiero que discutamos los detalles en el cuartel general, si es que tenéis "
"alguno por ahora."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/preparation_01"
msgid ""
"Listen up, lads! We are to hold this bridge until the ground forces arrive. "
"Could be hours, could be days. No one knows. The only thing I know is that "
"Jerry has to take this bridge brick by brick if they want it."
msgstr ""
"¡Escuchen, muchachos! Debemos defender este puente hasta que lleguen las "
"fuerzas terrestres. Podrían ser horas, podrían ser días. Nadie lo sabe. Lo "
"único que sé es que los alemanes tendrán que tomar este puente ladrillo a "
"ladrillo si lo quieren."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/preparation_02"
msgid ""
"We’re completely surrounded, gentlemen. That simplifies our problem. Shoot "
"everything that moves and expect enemy attacks from all directions."
msgstr ""
"Estamos completamente rodeados, señores. Eso simplifica nuestro problema. "
"Disparad a todo lo que se mueva y esperad ataques enemigos desde todas las "
"direcciones."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/preparation_03"
msgid ""
"Remember, this is the job we have been trained for. The eyes of the world "
"are upon us. Let us show them what the Airborne can do."
msgstr ""
"Recordad que este es el trabajo para el que habéis sido entrenados. Los ojos "
"del mundo están puestos en vosotros. Demostradles lo que pueden hacer las "
"fuerzas aerotransportadas."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/preparation_04"
msgid ""
"I have always appreciated your attitude, Sir Digby. However let us not "
"forget how short we are on supplies. Make every shot count and spare your "
"ammo."
msgstr ""
"Siempre he apreciado tu actitud, Sir Digby. Sin embargo, no olvidemos que "
"andamos escasos de suministros. Aprovecha cada disparo y ahorra munición."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/preparation_05"
msgid ""
"In case you decide to take positions in houses… For God’s sake, please watch "
"your head while going upstairs. These bloody stairs will take us out quicker "
"than the Germans."
msgstr ""
"En caso de que decidan tomar posiciones en las casas... Por el amor de Dios, "
"tengan cuidado con la cabeza al subir las escaleras. Estas malditas "
"escaleras nos matarán antes que los alemanes."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/resistance_01"
msgid ""
"Goedemorgen friends, we are the local resistance fighters. Can’t miss the "
"chance to throw occupants off our land."
msgstr ""
"Buenos días, amigos, somos los combatientes de la resistencia local. No "
"podemos perder la oportunidad de expulsar a los ocupantes de nuestras "
"tierras."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/resistance_02"
msgid ""
"How can we assist you? We know every corner of this city and could help you "
"either on the battlefield or go look for some ammunition and weapons."
msgstr ""
"¿En qué podemos ayudarte? Conocemos cada rincón de esta ciudad y podemos "
"ayudarte tanto en el campo de batalla como a buscar municiones y armas."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/resistance_ammo"
msgid ""
"Got it. My people will come back soon, you will not regret. We won’t let you "
"down."
msgstr ""
"Entendido. Mi gente volverá pronto, no te arrepentirás. No te defraudaremos."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/resistance_joined"
msgid ""
"It’s an honor for us to fight back the occupiers together with you. We won’t "
"let you down."
msgstr ""
"Es un honor para nosotros luchar contra los ocupantes junto a ustedes. No "
"los defraudaremos."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/preparation_artstrike_start"
msgid ""
"They are firing artillery at our positions! Take cover at our defensive "
"positions!"
msgstr ""
"¡Están disparando artillería contra nuestras posiciones! ¡Pónganse a "
"cubierto en nuestras posiciones defensivas!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/preparation_artstrike_done"
msgid ""
"We haven't got much time, make sure we are ready to meet the German forces "
"very soon."
msgstr ""
"No tenemos mucho tiempo, asegúrate de que estemos listos para enfrentarnos a "
"las fuerzas alemanas muy pronto."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/part02_01"
msgid ""
"Is that all? I expected something more serious, not a few token infantrymen."
msgstr ""
"¿Eso es todo? Esperaba algo más serio, no unos pocos soldados de infantería "
"simbólicos."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/part02_02"
msgid "Those poor sods must’ve been probing our defenses."
msgstr "Esos pobres desgraciados debían de estar sondeando nuestras defensas."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/part02_03"
msgid ""
"Gentlemen, I’ve received a spot of good news. Thirty Corps and the American "
"82nd are advancing towards the bridge at Nijmegen. We might get relief even "
"sooner as we thought."
msgstr ""
"Señores, he recibido buenas noticias. El 30.º Cuerpo y la 82.ª División "
"estadounidense avanzan hacia el puente de Nimega. Es posible que recibamos "
"ayuda antes de lo que pensábamos."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/part02_04"
msgid ""
"Sir, if I'm correct, then the ground forces will be here in a couple hours."
msgstr ""
"Señor, si no me equivoco, las fuerzas terrestres llegarán aquí en un par de "
"horas."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/part02_05"
msgid ""
"The whole show hangs on what we do today. If we make it, we might just wrap "
"up the war by Christmas. Think of the lives saved."
msgstr ""
"Todo depende de lo que hagamos hoy. Si lo logramos, podríamos terminar la "
"guerra antes de Navidad. Piensa en las vidas que se salvarán."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/part03_01"
msgid ""
"Everyone, take cover in basements! They are rolling out rocket artillery!"
msgstr ""
"¡Todos, refugiaos en los sótanos! ¡Están lanzando artillería con cohetes!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/part03_02"
msgid "I have one of my best squads on the other side. They’ll do their best."
msgstr ""
"Tengo a uno de mis mejores equipos al otro lado. Harán todo lo posible."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/part03_03"
msgid ""
"Let’s be very careful, these are elite troops. First, we have to distract "
"them before they fire."
msgstr ""
"Tengamos mucho cuidado, son tropas de élite. Primero, tenemos que "
"distraerlos antes de que disparen."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/part03_04"
msgid ""
"Look, the Germans have left some explosive charges here. That’s exactly what "
"we need."
msgstr ""
"Mirad, los alemanes han dejado aquí unas cargas explosivas. Eso es justo lo "
"que necesitamos."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/part03_05"
msgid ""
"Fantastic job, people. We should get the hell out of here before their "
"reinforcements arrive."
msgstr ""
"Buen trabajo, chicos. Tenemos que largarnos de aquí antes de que lleguen los "
"refuerzos."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/part04_01"
msgid ""
"I cannot believe they made it… Now all the odds to hold this city are on our "
"side!"
msgstr ""
"No puedo creer que lo hayan conseguido... ¡Ahora todas las probabilidades de "
"mantener esta ciudad están de vuestro lado!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/part04_02"
msgid ""
"Seems like the Corps is stuck on its way. We have to hold a little longer."
msgstr ""
"Parece que el Cuerpo de Marines se ha quedado atascado en el camino. Tenemos "
"que aguantar un poco más."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/part04_03"
msgid "Damn, I’ve been hit!"
msgstr "¡Maldición, me han dado!"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/part04_ammo"
msgid ""
"The resistance has brought us this truck. They said to take a look inside."
msgstr ""
"La resistencia nos ha traído este camión. Dijeron que echáramos un vistazo "
"dentro."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/cutscene/outro_01"
msgid "They will not come for us, will they?"
msgstr "No vendrán a por nosotros, ¿verdad?"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/narrator/cutscene/outro_02"
msgid "Tell them to lower their weapons… Our fight is over…"
msgstr "Díganles que bajen las armas... Nuestra lucha ha terminado..."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/tasks/01_bridge"
msgid "Secure the bridge"
msgstr "Asegura el puente."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/tasks/02_hq"
msgid "Hold the HQ building at all costs"
msgstr "Defender el edificio del cuartel general a toda costa."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/tasks/03_nebelwerfer"
msgid "Destroy the Nebelwerfer battery"
msgstr "Destruye la batería Nebelwerfer."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/tasks/opt01_workshop"
msgid "Hold the workshop facilities"
msgstr "Reserva las instalaciones del taller."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/tasks/opt02_prison"
msgid "Hold the prison building"
msgstr "Retén el edificio de la prisión."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/tasks/opt03_jeeppark"
msgid "Hold the jeep park"
msgstr "Mantén el parque de jeeps"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/tasks/opt04_b_east"
msgid "Hold the eastern bridge"
msgstr "Mantén el puente oriental."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/tasks/opt04_b_west"
msgid "Hold the western bridge"
msgstr "Mantén el puente occidental"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/tasks/opt06_district"
msgid "Hold the residential area"
msgstr "Mantén la zona residencial."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/tasks/opt07_factory"
msgid "Hold the factory facilities"
msgstr "Mantener las instalaciones de la fábrica."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/tasks/opt08_post"
msgid "Hold the outpost"
msgstr "Mantén el puesto avanzado."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/tasks/opt_resistance_ammo_completed"
msgid "I'll take two - Ask the Dutch resistance squad to find more ammunition"
msgstr ""
"Me llevaré dos. Pide al escuadrón de la resistencia holandesa que busque más "
"munición."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/tasks/"
"opt_resistance_recruit_completed"
msgid "Doomed Tea Party - Recruit the Dutch resistance squad"
msgstr "Doomed Tea Party: recluta al escuadrón de la resistencia holandesa."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/tasks/secret01"
msgid "Secret objective #1"
msgstr "Objetivo secreto nº 1"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/tasks/secret01_completed"
msgid ""
"Secret objective: Why die for Arnhem? - Make German garrison retreat without "
"fight"
msgstr ""
"Objetivo secreto: ¿Por qué morir por Arnhem? - Hacer que la guarnición "
"alemana se retire sin luchar."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/tasks/secret02"
msgid "Secret objective #2"
msgstr "Objetivo secreto n.º 2"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/tasks/secret02_completed"
msgid ""
"Secret objective: Career shift - After loosing all AT guns, give a PIAT to "
"any of your former AT gun crew"
msgstr ""
"Objetivo secreto: Cambio de carrera. Después de perder todos los cañones "
"antitanque, entrega un PIAT a cualquiera de tus antiguas tripulaciones de "
"cañones antitanque."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/ui/loose_nebelwerfer"
msgid "You did not destroy the artillery in time."
msgstr "No destruiste la artillería a tiempo."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/ui/loose_units_lost"
msgid "You lost all your units."
msgstr "Has perdido todas tus unidades."

#, boost-format
msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/ui/obj_progress_reinf"
msgid "Allied forces are %1% km away"
msgstr "Las fuerzas aliadas están a %1% km de distancia."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/ui/reinf_resistance_ammo"
msgid "Search for ammo"
msgstr "Buscar munición"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/ui/reinf_resistance_ammo_hint"
msgid ""
"Send the Dutch Resistance squad to search for ammunition. They will come "
"back later with their findings."
msgstr ""
"Envía al escuadrón de la Resistencia holandesa a buscar municiones. Volverán "
"más tarde con lo que hayan encontrado."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/ui/reinf_resistance_join"
msgid "Join us"
msgstr "Únete a nosotros"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/ui/reinf_resistance_join_hint"
msgid ""
"The Dutch Resistance squad becomes playable for the rest of this mission."
msgstr ""
"El escuadrón de la Resistencia holandesa estará disponible para jugar "
"durante el resto de esta misión."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/ui/reinf_skip_preparation"
msgid "Skip preparation"
msgstr "Saltar preparación"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/ui/timer_nebelwerfer"
msgid "Distract artillery men before they fire"
msgstr "Distrae a los artilleros antes de que disparen."

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/ui/timer_preparation"
msgid "Arrival of German mechanized forces"
msgstr "Llegada de las fuerzas mecanizadas alemanas"

msgctxt "mission/single/05-eng/1944_09_17_arnhem/ui/hint_choice"
msgid ""
"The Dutch Resistance squad is willing to help you. Choose one of the options "
"in the <c(B29557)>reinforcements tab</c>."
msgstr ""
"El escuadrón de la resistencia holandesa está dispuesto a ayudarte. Elige "
"una de las opciones en la pestaña «Refuerzos» de <c(B29557)></c> ."
